OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780427468
OL,3,CThousands still have 'intermittent
OL,4,Csupplies' as drinking water returns
OL,6,FSouth East Water say drinking water
OL,7,Fsupply has been restored for all
OL,8,Fcustomers across Kent but over 2000
OL,9,Fpeople in the county are still
OL,10,Fexperiencing intermittent supply
OL,11,Fissues, over a week since problems
OL,12,Ffirst began.
OL,14,FThe company said that a burst water
OL,15,Fpipe in Whitstable has caused
OL,16,Fcustomers in the area to have low
OL,17,Fpressure or lose water supply entirely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
