OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780427468
OL,3,CThousands still have 'intermittent
OL,4,Csupplies' as drinking water returns
OL,6,FThey added that around 2,200 in the
OL,7,FCoxheath, Headcorn and Ulcombe areas
OL,8,Fof Kent are having supply issues, but
OL,9,Fthat the situation is improving and
OL,10,Fthey are doing everything they can to
OL,11,Faddress the situation.
OL,13,FThe company's Incident Manager, Steve
OL,14,FBenton also urged customers to only
OL,15,Fuse water for essential purposes, such
OL,16,Fas drinking, cooking and hygiene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
